        <div class="why-gold-bar"></div>
        <h3 class="why-box-heading">You Speak Directly With Your Lawyer</h3>
        <p class="why-box-desc">Shawn Sidhu handles every case personally. You will not be passed off to a junior associate or a paralegal. When you have questions, you get real answers from the person managing your file.</p>
