<section class="at-section" id="accident-types">
  <div class="at-inner" style="max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 2.5rem">
    <div class="at-header" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0">
      <span class="section-label">Cases We Handle</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem" data-stc="accidents_city">Types of Accidents We Handle in Maple Ridge</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted,#6b7280);font-size:0.95rem;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.8">If you were injured in Maple Ridge, we can help. We handle all types of personal injury cases on a contingency basis — you pay nothing unless we win. Tap any case type to learn more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flat-practice-grid">
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1747930838451-1f9c3a8ea057?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_car">Car &amp; Truck Accidents</h3><p data-pd="pd_car">Injured in a car or truck accident in Maple Ridge? ICBC will try to minimize your payout. We fight back so you receive the full settlement you deserve, not what they want to pay.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757175-5700dde675bc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_brain">Brain &amp; Catastrophic Injuries</h3><p data-pd="pd_brain">Serious injuries demand serious representation. We pursue maximum compensation for brain injuries, spinal injuries, and other catastrophic harm caused by another's negligence.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487754336554-9809144112a6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_slip">Slip and Fall</h3><p data-pd="pd_slip">Property owners have a legal duty to keep premises safe. If negligence caused your fall in Maple Ridge, you may be entitled to significant compensation.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567613074247-5e2564e1b90a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_moto">Motorcycle Accidents</h3><p data-pd="pd_moto">Riders face unique risks and insurer bias. We level the playing field and pursue every dollar of compensation available to Maple Ridge motorcycle accident victims.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1642350371707-510555b9c478?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_death">Wrongful Death</h3><p data-pd="pd_death">If you've lost a loved one due to someone else's negligence, we pursue full compensation on behalf of your family with compassion and determination.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581090122319-8fab9528eaaa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_ltd">LTD Claim Denials</h3><p data-pd="pd_ltd">Insurance companies routinely deny legitimate long-term disability claims. We challenge those decisions and fight for the benefits you paid for.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1623261887667-dfa1b90422a0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_ped">Pedestrian Accidents</h3><p data-pd="pd_ped">Pedestrians struck by vehicles face serious injuries. We fight for full compensation including medical costs, lost income, and long-term care.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502744688674-c619d1586c9e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_bike">Bicycle Accidents</h3><p data-pd="pd_bike">Cyclists are among the most vulnerable road users. If you were hit by a vehicle, you deserve maximum compensation for your injuries.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587300003388-59208cc962cb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_dog">Dog Bites, Animal Attacks &amp; Burns</h3><p data-pd="pd_dog">Animal owners are liable for injuries their pets cause. Burn victims also have strong legal claims. We pursue full compensation for physical injuries, scarring, and trauma.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449965408869-eaa3f722e40d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_ride">Rideshare Accidents</h3><p data-pd="pd_ride">Injured in an Uber or Lyft? Insurance coverage in rideshare cases is complex. We navigate it so you don't have to.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160607-ee22621dd758?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_product">Product Liability</h3><p data-pd="pd_product">Defective products that cause injury create manufacturer liability. We hold companies accountable when their products harm you.</p></div>
      <div class="flat-practice-card flat-practice-extra" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')"><h3 data-pc="pc_med">Medical Malpractice</h3><p data-pd="pd_med">When healthcare providers fail in their duty of care, the consequences can be life-altering. We fight for victims of medical negligence.</p></div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center"><button class="flat-see-more" onclick="flatToggle(this)">See More Practice Areas &#8964;</button></div>
  </div>
  <script>function flatToggle(btn){var cards=document.querySelectorAll('.flat-practice-extra');var open=btn.classList.toggle('open');cards.forEach(function(c){c.classList.toggle('visible',open);});btn.innerHTML=open?'See Less &#8963;':'See More Practice Areas &#8964;';}</script>
</section>

